---
title: Marmalade Sticky Chicken with Butter-Glazed Vegetables
description: Chicken legs are brushed with the easiest and most flavourful glaze ever, thanks to the magic combination of marmalade and hoisin sauce! Paired with sweet butter-glazed veggies, this recipe is sure to be a family favourite.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/marmalade-sticky-chicken-91adc9f9.jpg
